  "description": "A breathtaking sunset scene over a coastal city and bay. The sun is positioned low on the horizon, partially obscured by a layer of clouds, casting a vibrant golden and orange glow across the sky. The sky is filled with dynamic cloud formations, ranging in color from bright yellow and orange near the sun to deep blues and purples higher up. Below the sky, a sprawling cityscape is visible, with buildings and infrastructure blending into the overall landscape. A long bridge stretches across the bay, connecting landmasses in the distance. Silhouetted hills and mountains form the backdrop, adding depth to the scene. In the foreground, the dark silhouette of trees adds a framing element.",
